race.comment: RONNY ROCK ART (6) sharp form reversal when sitting on the pace for a fighting second over 1400m at Warwick Farm in BM72 class. Winning apprentice hops back aboard and will prove hard to get past. FELIS CHAUS (9) is starting to hit his straps this campaign and like the way he attacked the line when sixth over 1400m at Warwick Farm. Hard fit now and can get cover from the draw.  HETZENDORF (10) dominant return when a slick maiden winner over 1300m at this track. Blinkers go on and worth thought in this stronger contest. HELLOVA NATURE (3) drops a few levels for this and has a victory at this track. Gripped on late when fourth over 1500m at Port Macquarie. Maps to get the right run.
